## Output Format

Report each finding on a SINGLE LINE in this exact pipe-delimited format:

```
FINDING|line:{line_number}|severity:{critical|major|minor}|category:grammar|current:{exact problematic text}|fix:{your suggested fix}|explanation:{brief explanation}
```

Examples:
```
FINDING|line:42|severity:major|category:grammar|current:The argument suggest that|fix:The argument suggests that|explanation:Subject-verb agreement error
FINDING|line:103|severity:critical|category:grammar|current:Having examined the results. The conclusion|fix:Having examined the results, the conclusion|explanation:Sentence fragment followed by dangling modifier
```

Report at most **10 findings** for this chunk. Prioritize by severity.

If this chunk has no grammar issues, output exactly: `NO_FINDINGS`
